TITLE: Optimizing resolveData with Change Detection in Puck
DESCRIPTION: Example of optimizing resolveData by only updating when specific props change. This implementation only updates resolvedTitle when the title prop has changed.
SOURCE: https://github.com/measuredco/puck/blob/main/apps/docs/pages/docs/api-reference/configuration/component-config.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_10

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
